1
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:12,750
I know that after you woke up,

2
00:02:12,750 --> 00:02:14,150
you would want to see the general first.

3
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:14,750
So...

4
00:02:14,910 --> 00:02:16,970
Where is the medicine I brought back?

5
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:19,240
You were holding it so tightly,

6
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,430
refusing to let go.

7
00:02:29,870 --> 00:02:30,910
Xiao Chi,

8
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,960
look what I brought back.

9
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,750
Don't worry,

10
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:39,000
you will wake up soon.

11
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:36,000
Why doesn't it work?

12
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,630
Your Majesty, since we left the palace,

13
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:46,240
you've kept my eyes blindfolded.

14
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:48,040
Where exactly are you taking me?

15
00:03:49,079 --> 00:03:50,079
This is the place.

16
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,910
This street is so beautiful at night.

17
00:03:56,910 --> 00:03:57,750
It's alright.

18
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,080
But

19
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,360
why is there no one around?

20
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:11,290
I told the vendors to go home early.

21
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:12,680
But

22
00:04:12,870 --> 00:04:14,400
I bought all their goods.

23
00:04:16,190 --> 00:04:18,050
Why did you do that, Your Majesty?

24
00:04:18,269 --> 00:04:20,399
I've always envied the common people.

25
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:21,560
They

26
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:23,480
can take their loved ones

27
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,830
and stroll through the market.

28
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,480
They can also

29
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,950
pick out some little items

30
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:30,680
handmade by the small vendors.

31
00:04:30,870 --> 00:04:32,200
It's very interesting.

32
00:04:32,830 --> 00:04:35,270
You didn't have to buy everything, though.

33
00:04:35,270 --> 00:04:37,430
Well, I couldn't just
chase them home.

34
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:39,840
By the way,

35
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,100
in a couple of days,

36
00:04:41,270 --> 00:04:43,070
the delegation from Changmo
will be arriving.

37
00:04:43,070 --> 00:04:44,159
You can pick

38
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:46,190
some things you like here,

39
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:48,360
or things you find interesting,

40
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:49,750
and have them take them back.

41
00:04:49,750 --> 00:04:50,920
Consider it

42
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,040
a return gift,

43
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:52,560
okay?

44
00:04:52,630 --> 00:04:53,270
Really?

45
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:56,950
Then I'll have them take it all away,

46
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:58,390
and let the people of Changmo

47
00:04:58,390 --> 00:05:00,480
see just how bustling
these streets can be.

48
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,120
Sure.

49
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:02,430
They can take it all away.

50
00:05:02,430 --> 00:05:03,160
You said it.

51
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:03,630
Yeah.

52
00:05:14,830 --> 00:05:15,480
Take this.

53
00:05:20,630 --> 00:05:21,510
You wear this.

54
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:22,600
Yeah.

55
00:05:51,870 --> 00:05:52,680
Let's go.

56
00:06:11,070 --> 00:06:12,430
The medical hall's business is good.

57
00:06:12,430 --> 00:06:13,890
Any good medicinal herbs?

58
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:14,870
Uncle Lie.

59
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:17,800
Why are you here?

60
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,680
You wouldn't go back to Changmo,

61
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,680
so of course I came to see you myself.

62
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:21,630
Now,

63
00:06:21,630 --> 00:06:23,190
the two countries have
formed a marriage alliance,

64
00:06:23,190 --> 00:06:24,480
and the borders have opened for trade.

65
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,160
I came

66
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:27,160
with the merchant caravan from Fengyang.

67
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,600
For one thing, they told me

68
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,430
there's a very good medical hall
in the north of the city,

69
00:06:30,430 --> 00:06:31,800
and the physician is very skilled,

70
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,190
who seems to have cured

71
00:06:33,190 --> 00:06:34,240
a plague in some village.

72
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:36,570
Of course I had to come
and learn from them.

73
00:06:36,870 --> 00:06:38,680
Uncle Lie, you're making fun of me.

74
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,510
Not at all.

75
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:43,159
I found Mo.

76
00:06:43,430 --> 00:06:45,680
But I settled him
in a bamboo grove cottage,

77
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,870
and haven't brought him over yet.

78
00:06:46,870 --> 00:06:47,830
You found Mo?

79
00:06:47,830 --> 00:06:49,070
How is he doing now?

80
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:51,190
He has suffered a lot over the years.

81
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,159
He hasn't woken up yet.

82
00:06:53,390 --> 00:06:54,390
Thanks to Xiao Chi.

83
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:55,120
Otherwise, I wouldn't have been able

84
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,830
to save him alone.

85
00:06:58,430 --> 00:06:59,480
Xiao Chi?

86
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:02,140
Then I should find a chance

87
00:07:02,310 --> 00:07:04,240
to thank him.

88
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:05,830
By the way,

89
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:07,680
I live in Jie'an Ward
in the south of the city.

90
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,740
Tomorrow morning.

91
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:10,390
Bring Mo over early in the morning,

92
00:07:10,390 --> 00:07:11,790
so I can help him recover.

93
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,390
Great.

94
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:16,870
I see you

95
00:07:16,870 --> 00:07:18,430
have lost a lot of weight since last time.

96
00:07:18,430 --> 00:07:19,920
Is something on your mind?

97
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,310
Don't worry.

98
00:07:21,630 --> 00:07:22,560
With me here,

99
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,070
anything can be solved.

100
00:07:24,830 --> 00:07:25,360
Mhm.

101
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:27,270
I have things to do, so I'll get going.

102
00:07:27,270 --> 00:07:28,070
Mhm.

103
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:42,159
Uncle Lie is here.

104
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:44,790
He will definitely be
able to cure Xiao Chi.

105
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:02,070
Come out.

106
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,160
It's been a while, Fei Zheng.

107
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:10,950
Hall Master.

108
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:14,000
When did you arrive in the capital?

109
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,600
The marriage alliance went smoothly.

110
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,680
The borders are open.

111
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,120
The tribute envoys coming to the capital

112
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,580
had an unimpeded journey.

113
00:08:20,190 --> 00:08:22,590
Lord Fei, you deserve
some credit for this.

114
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:26,630
I've done everything I was supposed to.

115
00:08:26,630 --> 00:08:27,830
What more do you want?

116
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:30,240
You really think you've
grown strong enough

117
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:32,360
to escape Changmo's control?

118
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:33,870
Don't forget,

119
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,480
you are a spy sent by Changmo to Jinglan.

120
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:40,409
Now, whether it's for Changmo or Jinglan,

121
00:08:40,549 --> 00:08:42,720
I only hope the 2 countries
can have everlasting peace.

122
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,669
Peace?

123
00:08:45,030 --> 00:08:46,080
I think you are just reluctant to give up

124
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:48,240
your position
as an important court minister.

125
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,240
Say what you will.

126
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:52,410
All these years, I have a clear conscience

127
00:08:52,510 --> 00:08:53,550
towards Changmo.

128
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,390
A clear conscience?

129
00:08:57,630 --> 00:08:58,750
What about Jin Xi?

130
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:01,080
Do you have
a clear conscience towards her, too?

131
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:03,480
You led her onto
the path of becoming a spy.

132
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:06,480
Then please show mercy, Hall Master.

133
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,360
Give her the antidote,

134
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,440
spare her life,

135
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,770
and return her freedom.

136
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:13,080
She can't run away.

137
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,330
And neither can you.

138
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:19,740
What exactly are you
trying to say, Hall Master?

139
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,080
In the Jinglan court,

140
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:24,080
I need someone more obedient.

141
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,790
Ask Li Shichang out.

142
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,960
Otherwise,

143
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,390
I'll let the Emperor of Jinglan

144
00:09:28,390 --> 00:09:30,080
know your true identity.

145
00:09:30,670 --> 00:09:31,630
Let's see then

146
00:09:31,630 --> 00:09:33,510
if he still acknowledges
you as his second brother.

147
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:34,360
Meng Ling.

148
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:39,550
Fine.

149
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:41,880
If I agree to your terms,

150
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:44,600
you must give the antidote to Jin Xi.

151
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,200
Sure.

152
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,280
This is the last time.

153
00:09:56,670 --> 00:09:57,150
Come on,

154
00:09:57,390 --> 00:09:58,150
Lord Li.

155
00:09:58,390 --> 00:09:59,190
A toast to you.

156
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,360
You must be joking, Lord Fei.

157
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,720
It's my honor to share a drink

158
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,240
with one of Jinglan's finest

159
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,670
under such

160
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:11,480
a lovely night.

161
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:35,150
Why is she here?

162
00:10:36,750 --> 00:10:37,670
Lord Fei,

163
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:40,550
you seem to have a special liking

164
00:10:40,550 --> 00:10:42,000
for this dancer.

165
00:10:43,790 --> 00:10:45,550
You must be joking, Lord Li.

166
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:47,240
I simply think

167
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:50,480
this dancer's style is quite unique.

168
00:10:52,670 --> 00:10:53,320
Lord Fei,

169
00:10:53,630 --> 00:10:55,790
you must be joking.

170
00:10:56,390 --> 00:10:58,360
This dancer's performance

171
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,870
is quite average.

172
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:02,320
Even her most basic steps

173
00:11:02,670 --> 00:11:04,870
are not on the beat.

174
00:11:06,870 --> 00:11:08,440
Although her dancing

175
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:10,360
is not great,

176
00:11:10,870 --> 00:11:12,120
fortunately,

177
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:13,630
she is pretty

178
00:11:13,630 --> 00:11:15,200
and gentle.

179
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:17,700
I seem to have seen her somewhere before.

180
00:11:33,030 --> 00:11:33,670
Jin Xi,

181
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:35,200
it really is you.

182
00:11:35,550 --> 00:11:36,840
Why are you here?

183
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,600
Lord Fei,

184
00:11:38,870 --> 00:11:41,400
you are still as naive
as when you were a child.

185
00:11:53,670 --> 00:11:54,870
You put a Gu inside me?

186
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,270
Despicable.

187
00:11:57,270 --> 00:11:59,670
Those who achieve great things
don't bother about trifles.

188
00:11:59,670 --> 00:12:01,800
This Gu poison will act up once a month.

189
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,480
And it feels terrible.

190
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:05,670
Will you listen to me now?

191
00:12:07,670 --> 00:12:09,470
You must be joking, Hall Master.

192
00:12:09,670 --> 00:12:11,480
Of all the missions sent
from Changmo over the years,

193
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,510
which one wasn't completed by me

194
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:13,870
with hard work?

195
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,100
I have never forgotten

196
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:17,840
my oath to Changmo.

197
00:12:19,670 --> 00:12:21,600
If what you say is true,

198
00:12:21,870 --> 00:12:24,480
I will naturally give you
an antidote every month.

199
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:26,200
But as for this antidote now,

200
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,660
will you take it yourself,

201
00:12:27,870 --> 00:12:29,150
or give it to her?

202
00:12:30,030 --> 00:12:30,870
You choose.

203
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,440
Jin Xi is nothing

204
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:44,240
but a tool to me.

205
00:12:50,030 --> 00:12:51,670
Men are all like this.

206
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:01,390
Jin Xi.

207
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:04,000
Jin Xi.

208
00:13:06,150 --> 00:13:07,270
Has it really

209
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:09,840
come to this between us?

210
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:38,870
These were all sent
by the Changmo delegation?

211
00:13:38,870 --> 00:13:39,630
Yes.

212
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:41,840
This is unique to Changmo.

213
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:43,320
It's called a pomegranate.

214
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:43,670
Oh.

215
00:13:43,670 --> 00:13:44,480
And this.

216
00:13:45,270 --> 00:13:46,550
This is called a fig.

217
00:13:46,550 --> 00:13:48,410
It looks like a mini pomegranate.

218
00:13:48,750 --> 00:13:49,550
And this.

219
00:13:50,030 --> 00:13:51,690
This is called a yellow peach.

220
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:53,910
There are gold and silver,

221
00:13:53,910 --> 00:13:55,200
furs and fine clothes,

222
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:56,800
and these specialty fruits.

223
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,360
Seeing them

224
00:13:58,910 --> 00:14:00,750
is like returning to Changmo.

225
00:14:02,670 --> 00:14:03,510
My love.

226
00:14:04,270 --> 00:14:05,200
Missing home?

227
00:14:08,790 --> 00:14:10,960
Home is wherever you are.

228
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:13,910
How about next time,

229
00:14:13,910 --> 00:14:16,480
we ask your father
to come with the delegation?

230
00:14:16,480 --> 00:14:19,140
I've always wanted to have
a good drink with him.

231
00:14:20,030 --> 00:14:21,560
My father is in poor health.

232
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:23,730
He might not be able to travel that far.

233
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:25,640
That doesn't matter.

234
00:14:26,030 --> 00:14:28,790
Then next time I will
accompany you back to Changmo

235
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:30,050
to visit him properly.

236
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:38,060
You're sleepy in broad daylight?

237
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:40,760
I've been eating
and sleeping a lot lately.

238
00:14:42,270 --> 00:14:43,150
I was thinking,

239
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:45,440
could I be

240
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:47,030
pregnant?

241
00:14:49,870 --> 00:14:51,030
What did you say?

242
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:58,960
This is great news
for Jinglan and Changmo!

243
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:02,080
I will announce it to the world tomorrow

244
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:04,080
and let everyone know the good news.

245
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:05,790
Don't rush.

246
00:15:06,390 --> 00:15:07,360
It's so embarrassing.

247
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:08,480
I'm not sure yet.

248
00:15:08,630 --> 00:15:10,750
What's there to be embarrassed about?

249
00:15:10,750 --> 00:15:13,000
This is the first child of you and me.

250
00:15:13,670 --> 00:15:15,630
Whether it's a boy or a girl,

251
00:15:15,870 --> 00:15:17,390
I will protect them well.

252
00:15:18,270 --> 00:15:19,390
I want them

253
00:15:20,030 --> 00:15:22,150
to come into this world safely.

254
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:24,490
I will teach them how to read and write.

255
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,790
If it's a boy,

256
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:28,440
I will

257
00:15:29,390 --> 00:15:30,320
give him a title,

258
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:32,330
let him inherit my throne,

259
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:35,440
and let him govern Jinglan well.

260
00:15:36,270 --> 00:15:37,600
And if it's a girl?

261
00:15:39,670 --> 00:15:41,080
If it's a girl,

262
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,120
we will

263
00:15:43,910 --> 00:15:45,600
find her a good husband,

264
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:47,870
marry her off in style,

265
00:15:48,360 --> 00:15:49,890
and make her as happy as you.

266
00:15:51,630 --> 00:15:52,360
And then?

267
00:15:52,870 --> 00:15:53,550
Then...

268
00:15:54,510 --> 00:15:55,570
Then we keep going.

269
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:56,870
Keep going?

270
00:15:57,550 --> 00:15:59,880
You thought you could
just have one or two?

271
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,030
I will definitely make you

272
00:16:01,030 --> 00:16:02,030
have 10 or 20 kids

273
00:16:02,030 --> 00:16:02,840
before I let you go.

274
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:04,200
Ten or twenty?

275
00:16:04,670 --> 00:16:05,550
I'm not a mouse.

276
00:16:05,550 --> 00:16:07,120
How could I have that many?

277
00:16:11,080 --> 00:16:11,750
Miss,

278
00:16:11,750 --> 00:16:13,200
come take a look at the fruit.

279
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:14,870
All fine fruits from Changmo.

280
00:16:22,030 --> 00:16:24,600
It's rare to see such large pomegranates.

281
00:16:25,080 --> 00:16:26,870
You really know your stuff, Miss.

282
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:28,470
Jinglan doesn't have these.

283
00:16:28,790 --> 00:16:30,650
Others don't know about them yet.

284
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:33,870
Would you like a taste?

285
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:35,030
No, thank you.

286
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,730
You look like a kind person.

287
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:40,630
Have a taste.

288
00:16:40,630 --> 00:16:41,790
I won't charge you.

289
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:45,030
Yunling.

290
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:47,820
I was just looking for you.

291
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:48,870
Uncle Lie.

292
00:16:51,870 --> 00:16:52,840
These

293
00:16:53,030 --> 00:16:54,670
were all shipped from Changmo, right?

294
00:16:54,670 --> 00:16:56,390
For such fine goods from afar,

295
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:58,450
you should sell them for a good price.

296
00:17:00,270 --> 00:17:01,550
I found a new antidote.

297
00:17:01,550 --> 00:17:03,210
You can take it back and try it.

298
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:04,550
Really?

299
00:17:04,550 --> 00:17:05,000
Yes.

300
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:06,000
Let's hurry back then.

301
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:06,530
Let's go.

302
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:36,240
This is the antidote pill
I brought back from Changmo.

303
00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:37,070
Give it

304
00:17:37,480 --> 00:17:38,640
to Xiao Chi.

305
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:40,720
Jinglan's arrow poison

306
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:42,070
shouldn't have changed.

307
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:43,160
Rest assured.

308
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:44,770
After taking this pill,

309
00:17:44,880 --> 00:17:46,340
he will surely get better.

310
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:47,930
If even this can't cure him,

311
00:17:49,030 --> 00:17:49,680
I'm afraid

312
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:51,200
no one in the world can.

313
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,440
Xiao Chi

314
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:56,590
not only saved you,

315
00:17:56,680 --> 00:17:57,880
but also saved my Mo.

316
00:17:58,790 --> 00:17:59,680
You know,

317
00:17:59,750 --> 00:18:00,400
I never

318
00:18:00,510 --> 00:18:02,270
want to owe anyone.

319
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:03,680
Thank you, Uncle Lie.

320
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:05,030
I'll go give it to him now.

321
00:18:05,030 --> 00:18:05,550
Go.

322
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:24,440
It smells so sweet.

323
00:18:24,590 --> 00:18:25,200
It must be my

324
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:26,070
Consort Ling.

325
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:27,680
When did you wake up?

326
00:18:27,680 --> 00:18:28,810
I woke up a while ago.

327
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:31,020
I woke up when you came in just now.

328
00:18:32,270 --> 00:18:33,510
I just wanted to see

329
00:18:33,830 --> 00:18:35,760
what kind of trick you'd play on me.

330
00:18:36,590 --> 00:18:38,160
What trick could I possibly play on you?

331
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:39,490
I don't know about that.

332
00:18:40,030 --> 00:18:40,920
But I have to let you

333
00:18:40,920 --> 00:18:41,790
know

334
00:18:42,030 --> 00:18:42,890
how bad I can be.

335
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:52,480
If you treat me badly,

336
00:18:52,590 --> 00:18:54,030
the baby and I won't let it go.

337
00:18:54,030 --> 00:18:55,030
Don't worry.

338
00:18:55,590 --> 00:18:56,850
For the rest of my life,

339
00:18:57,030 --> 00:18:59,270
I will treat you both very well.

340
00:19:02,680 --> 00:19:03,640
Look what I brought you.

341
00:19:03,640 --> 00:19:04,480
What is it?

342
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:06,640
This is tribute from our envoy.

343
00:19:06,830 --> 00:19:08,880
It's called Zhuyao in Changmo.

344
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:11,030
It's very rare.

345
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,240
Try one.

346
00:19:12,880 --> 00:19:14,280
How could I bear to eat it?

347
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:15,810
You can have it all.

348
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:17,200
Listen to me.

349
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:18,480
This Zhuyao

350
00:19:18,480 --> 00:19:19,550
is a custom among the women of Changmo.

351
00:19:19,550 --> 00:19:20,480
They feed them one by one

352
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:22,070
to the man they love,

353
00:19:22,070 --> 00:19:23,480
symbolizing eternal union

354
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:25,000
and the blessing of many children.

355
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:26,270
You have to eat it.

356
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:29,270
If you say so,

357
00:19:29,550 --> 00:19:31,440
I won't leave a single one for you.

358
00:19:33,350 --> 00:19:34,070
Then

359
00:19:34,750 --> 00:19:35,480
feed it to me.

360
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:25,830
Xiao Chi.

361
00:20:26,070 --> 00:20:28,160
This is my uncle's special antidote.

362
00:20:28,270 --> 00:20:29,600
It can cure all poisons.

363
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:31,750
You will be fine soon.

364
00:20:37,750 --> 00:20:38,310
Here.

365
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:28,830
You'll be fine.

366
00:21:37,750 --> 00:21:38,880
Strategist Mo Du,

367
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:41,030
what on earth are you thinking?

368
00:21:41,030 --> 00:21:42,350
Xiao Chi is injured now.

369
00:21:42,350 --> 00:21:43,590
Why did you save him?

370
00:21:45,030 --> 00:21:46,880
I don't like owing others.

371
00:21:47,200 --> 00:21:49,530
Just like when I fled
to Changmo back then,

372
00:21:49,880 --> 00:21:51,680
the King of Changmo did me a favor,

373
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:52,680
so

374
00:21:52,680 --> 00:21:54,880
I would pledge my life to him.

375
00:21:56,830 --> 00:21:58,640
I see that now you are back in Jinglan,

376
00:21:58,640 --> 00:21:59,880
this vow to pledge your life

377
00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:01,720
is thrown out of the window.

378
00:22:05,350 --> 00:22:06,350
Hall Master,

379
00:22:06,350 --> 00:22:08,030
just mind your own business.

380
00:22:08,160 --> 00:22:09,960
No need to interfere with mine.

381
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:13,480
You and I originally
had a division of labor.

382
00:22:13,790 --> 00:22:16,030
I make poison and spread it everywhere.

383
00:22:16,550 --> 00:22:17,480
And you,

384
00:22:17,830 --> 00:22:20,030
train spies and assassins.

385
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:21,920
You and I

386
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:24,070
stay out of each other's way.

387
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:26,270
Even if

388
00:22:27,350 --> 00:22:29,550
you have an affair with King of Changmo,

389
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:32,790
I don't need to follow your orders.

390
00:22:35,110 --> 00:22:36,030
Besides,

391
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:37,720
I'm the one who taught you

392
00:22:37,720 --> 00:22:39,250
all those Gu tricks you use.

393
00:22:39,270 --> 00:22:41,920
Although you've devoted
yourself to those things,

394
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:43,070
I've never thought

395
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:45,550
much of them.

396
00:22:53,270 --> 00:22:54,960
Then let's wait and see.

397
00:24:01,350 --> 00:24:02,350
Thank you.

398
00:24:13,030 --> 00:24:14,590
When did you wake up?

399
00:24:14,590 --> 00:24:15,160
I...

400
00:24:17,590 --> 00:24:18,400
Just now.

401
00:24:20,400 --> 00:24:21,350
Have you been

402
00:24:21,550 --> 00:24:23,280
taking care of me all this time?

403
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:24,640
Yeah.

404
00:24:28,680 --> 00:24:29,480
Now,

405
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:34,070
I really can't repay you.

406
00:24:35,960 --> 00:24:37,240
You don't look well.

407
00:24:38,590 --> 00:24:40,120
Do you want to go in and rest?

408
00:24:43,440 --> 00:24:44,700
Let me feel your pulse.

409
00:24:44,830 --> 00:24:45,680
Come in.

410
00:24:50,350 --> 00:24:51,240
Your Highness.

411
00:24:51,510 --> 00:24:53,440
Consort Ling seems to be pregnant.

412
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:54,510
Really?

413
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:57,240
I heard Consort Ling
tell His Majesty herself.

414
00:24:57,240 --> 00:24:58,550
It shouldn't be false.

415
00:24:58,790 --> 00:25:01,050
This is the first child of the Liu family.

416
00:25:01,590 --> 00:25:03,120
Whether it's a boy or a girl,

417
00:25:03,240 --> 00:25:04,590
it's a joyous event.

418
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:06,550
But Your Highness,

419
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:08,270
I am worried...

420
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:11,530
What are you worried about?

421
00:25:12,240 --> 00:25:13,160
Pregnancy

422
00:25:13,550 --> 00:25:15,160
takes 10 months.

423
00:25:16,270 --> 00:25:18,400
Come with me to Consort Ling's palace.

424
00:25:22,790 --> 00:25:23,590
What's wrong?

425
00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:28,030
Your Highness is fine.

426
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:30,440
And the fetus...

427
00:25:30,920 --> 00:25:32,450
What's wrong with the baby?

428
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:35,080
It's even healthier.

429
00:25:36,590 --> 00:25:38,720
You scared me to death, Physician Han.

430
00:25:40,550 --> 00:25:41,550
Physician Han.

431
00:25:41,720 --> 00:25:43,480
You've been taking care
of me all along the way.

432
00:25:43,480 --> 00:25:45,680
Now you have to take care of my child too.

433
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:48,640
It's my duty as a physician.

434
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:49,790
Besides,

435
00:25:49,830 --> 00:25:51,160
I also want to see

436
00:25:51,160 --> 00:25:53,690
what the lovely Princess's
child looks like.

437
00:25:55,510 --> 00:25:57,200
Then I also want to see

438
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:58,160
what the child of the beautiful physician

439
00:25:58,160 --> 00:25:59,440
and the heroic general

440
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:00,480
will look like.

441
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:01,640
Your Highness.

442
00:26:02,270 --> 00:26:03,240
If you keep saying that,

443
00:26:03,240 --> 00:26:04,970
I won't care about you anymore.

444
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:08,300
Where is Jin Xi?

445
00:26:10,110 --> 00:26:12,370
Princess Xie granted
Jin Xi a courtyard.

446
00:26:12,550 --> 00:26:14,010
She has already moved out.

447
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:16,000
Wanyu.

448
00:26:16,000 --> 00:26:17,830
Greetings, Your Highness.

449
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:19,350
Xie.

450
00:26:20,160 --> 00:26:21,690
Greetings, Your Highness.

451
00:26:21,830 --> 00:26:23,440
Dispense with the formalities.

452
00:26:23,440 --> 00:26:24,200
Wanyu.

453
00:26:24,720 --> 00:26:25,350
I...

454
00:26:25,350 --> 00:26:26,350
I specifically called a top gynecologist

455
00:26:26,350 --> 00:26:28,440
from the Imperial Medical Academy
to examine you.

456
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:29,720
So I can rest assured.

457
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:30,880
Thank you, Xie.

458
00:26:31,590 --> 00:26:32,850
This is Physician Han.

459
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:34,270
I was sick all the way from Changmo,

460
00:26:34,270 --> 00:26:35,530
and she took care of me.

461
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:38,480
With Physician Han taking care of you,

462
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:39,810
I am even more relieved.

463
00:26:40,240 --> 00:26:41,480
I will do my best.

464
00:26:42,270 --> 00:26:44,160
I will take my leave now.

465
00:26:44,550 --> 00:26:45,200
Okay.

466
00:26:48,350 --> 00:26:49,550
Sit down.

467
00:26:49,550 --> 00:26:50,350
Sit down, Xie.

468
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:55,170
Although Physician Han
is looking after you,

469
00:26:55,240 --> 00:26:56,480
you still need to

470
00:26:56,480 --> 00:26:58,790
pay close attention
to your own body at all times.

471
00:26:58,790 --> 00:26:59,880
Don't worry, Xie.

472
00:27:00,030 --> 00:27:00,790
I will.

473
00:27:00,790 --> 00:27:01,550
Come.

474
00:27:01,550 --> 00:27:02,350
Put it here.

475
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:04,350
I've

476
00:27:04,350 --> 00:27:06,000
prepared a little gift for you.

477
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:07,270
I hope you like it.

478
00:27:09,350 --> 00:27:10,030
This is...

479
00:27:10,240 --> 00:27:12,640
These are the clothes
His Majesty wore when he was a child.

480
00:27:12,640 --> 00:27:14,590
I've always kept them.

481
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:15,790
Now

482
00:27:15,790 --> 00:27:17,000
they come in handy.

483
00:27:18,640 --> 00:27:20,270
It's so cute!

484
00:27:20,270 --> 00:27:22,000
I'm glad you don't mind.

485
00:27:22,070 --> 00:27:23,480
How could I mind?

486
00:27:23,680 --> 00:27:25,640
These are the clothes Liu Chu wore.

487
00:27:27,350 --> 00:27:28,310
Thank you, Xie.

488
00:27:28,400 --> 00:27:29,720
You're welcome.

489
00:27:30,310 --> 00:27:31,480
Let me feel it.

490
00:27:31,480 --> 00:27:33,400
Xie, it's still small.

491
00:27:35,640 --> 00:27:36,680
Lord Li.

492
00:27:37,030 --> 00:27:38,200
Tasting tea

493
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:39,350
is like conducting oneself.

494
00:27:39,350 --> 00:27:40,200
A good cup of tea,

495
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:41,270
from boiling and brewing

496
00:27:41,270 --> 00:27:43,440
to the aroma unfolding,

497
00:27:43,750 --> 00:27:47,640
takes time and patience.

498
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:49,350
You are absolutely right, Lord Zhang.

499
00:27:49,350 --> 00:27:51,000
Your theory on tea

500
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:53,680
has completely convinced me.

501
00:27:53,750 --> 00:27:55,400
Wang Ruhai

502
00:27:55,400 --> 00:27:57,200
doesn't understand this.

503
00:27:57,830 --> 00:27:58,270
Please.

504
00:27:58,270 --> 00:27:59,030
My Lord.

505
00:27:59,350 --> 00:28:00,550
Something happened.

506
00:28:01,790 --> 00:28:02,510
What is it?

507
00:28:02,510 --> 00:28:03,790
Why the panic?

508
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:05,770
His Majesty has fallen ill.

509
00:28:07,200 --> 00:28:07,880
What?

510
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:09,110
How is this possible?

511
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:12,640
I am completely out of ideas.

512
00:28:12,720 --> 00:28:15,030
The problem is we
don't know what disease it is.

513
00:28:15,030 --> 00:28:16,270
So,

514
00:28:16,270 --> 00:28:17,310
what should we do?

515
00:28:17,880 --> 00:28:19,070
I can't tell.

516
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:31,410
Forgive me, Your Highness.

517
00:28:32,070 --> 00:28:34,200
There is no need to keep useless hands.

518
00:28:34,270 --> 00:28:35,110
Yes.

519
00:28:37,590 --> 00:28:38,510
Your Highness!

520
00:28:38,510 --> 00:28:40,970
What disease exactly
does His Majesty have?

521
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:42,000
Your Highness.

522
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:43,790
His Majesty's symptoms are unheard of.

523
00:28:43,790 --> 00:28:44,350
We...

524
00:28:44,550 --> 00:28:45,880
We haven't figured it out yet.

525
00:28:45,880 --> 00:28:47,340
You haven't figure it out?

526
00:28:47,590 --> 00:28:48,510
At this point,

527
00:28:48,510 --> 00:28:49,880
you still don't even know the cause.

528
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:51,240
What use are you?

529
00:28:54,200 --> 00:28:55,680
Please calm down, Your Highness.

530
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:56,510
We...

531
00:28:56,880 --> 00:28:59,110
We really have tried our best.

532
00:28:59,110 --> 00:29:00,920
Indeed.

533
00:29:07,310 --> 00:29:09,160
Summon Fei Zheng
and Xiao Chi to the palace.

534
00:29:09,160 --> 00:29:10,290
Yes, Your Highness.

535
00:29:18,590 --> 00:29:19,350
Xiao Chi.

536
00:29:19,590 --> 00:29:20,880
How are you feeling?

537
00:29:21,680 --> 00:29:23,400
Thank you for your concern, Your Highness.

538
00:29:23,400 --> 00:29:24,800
I am completely fine now.

539
00:29:25,270 --> 00:29:26,670
How about His Majesty...

540
00:29:27,790 --> 00:29:29,240
What did the imperial physicians say?

541
00:29:29,240 --> 00:29:30,160
Those quacks

542
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:32,110
say His Majesty seems ill but isn't,

543
00:29:32,110 --> 00:29:33,570
seems poisoned but isn't.

544
00:29:33,720 --> 00:29:35,830
The whole Imperial Medical Academy
is helpless.

545
00:29:35,830 --> 00:29:38,310
His Majesty's illness came
on very suddenly.

546
00:29:38,310 --> 00:29:39,830
Was His Majesty's food

547
00:29:40,590 --> 00:29:41,480
checked?

548
00:29:42,270 --> 00:29:43,680
His Majesty's daily routine

549
00:29:43,680 --> 00:29:45,080
is your responsibility.

550
00:29:45,200 --> 00:29:46,160
You tell me.

551
00:29:46,440 --> 00:29:47,510
Your Highness,

552
00:29:47,830 --> 00:29:50,270
His Majesty's daily routine
has been as usual lately.

553
00:29:50,270 --> 00:29:51,790
Everything His Majesty consumes

554
00:29:51,790 --> 00:29:53,200
is carefully examined.

555
00:29:53,270 --> 00:29:54,440
Only after confirming it is non-toxic

556
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:56,040
do we serve it to His Majesty.

557
00:29:56,440 --> 00:29:57,270
However...

558
00:29:57,270 --> 00:29:58,070
Speak.

559
00:29:58,680 --> 00:30:02,270
But a batch of food offered as tribute
by the Changmo delegation earlier

560
00:30:02,270 --> 00:30:04,200
was sent directly to Consort Ling.

561
00:30:04,200 --> 00:30:06,200
Although we have checked most of it,

562
00:30:06,720 --> 00:30:07,830
I'm just afraid...

563
00:30:10,510 --> 00:30:12,240
It's related to Changmo again.

564
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:14,540
Your Highness.

565
00:30:15,070 --> 00:30:16,920
The most important thing now is

566
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:18,640
to have His Majesty wake up quickly.

567
00:30:18,640 --> 00:30:20,110
Once His Majesty wakes up,

568
00:30:20,110 --> 00:30:21,720
whether it's poison or illness,

569
00:30:21,720 --> 00:30:23,000
we can investigate it however we want.

570
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:24,680
I wonder if Your Highness remembers

571
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:26,440
the physician who rendered
great service in Huangpi Village,

572
00:30:26,440 --> 00:30:27,270
Han Yunling.

573
00:30:29,790 --> 00:30:30,920
She previously

574
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:32,510
spent some time in Changmo.

575
00:30:32,920 --> 00:30:34,480
Perhaps having her treat
His Majesty in the palace

576
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:35,940
will yield some progress.

577
00:30:36,590 --> 00:30:38,510
So many senior imperial physicians
are helpless.

578
00:30:38,510 --> 00:30:40,170
Physician Han is still young.

579
00:30:40,270 --> 00:30:41,680
This is no joke.

580
00:30:43,510 --> 00:30:44,680
Your Highness,

581
00:30:44,720 --> 00:30:46,880
my illness was cured by Physician Han.

582
00:30:47,070 --> 00:30:49,640
Besides, we have no
other options at present.

583
00:30:50,270 --> 00:30:51,800
Perhaps we can give it a try.

584
00:30:52,310 --> 00:30:54,640
I beg Your Highness
to let Han Yunling try.

585
00:31:01,590 --> 00:31:02,160
Granted.

586
00:31:02,310 --> 00:31:03,070
You may rise.

587
00:31:03,310 --> 00:31:04,770
Thank you, Your Highness.

588
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:08,570
I don't know
when His Majesty will wake up.

589
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:10,680
You two must keep things steady.

590
00:31:10,680 --> 00:31:12,270
We can't let the court fall into chaos.

591
00:31:12,270 --> 00:31:13,400
Yes, Your Highness.

592
00:31:13,720 --> 00:31:15,920
I will stay here
to look after His Majesty.

593
00:31:15,920 --> 00:31:16,550
Xiao Chi,

594
00:31:17,110 --> 00:31:19,000
go bring Physician Han into the palace.

595
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:19,680
Fei Zheng,

596
00:31:20,270 --> 00:31:22,680
go investigate the cause of His Majesty's illness.

597
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:23,720
I accept your command.
